<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/58079842-miguel-ros"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/58079842-miguel-ros">Miguel Ros</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In the book, George is Richard&apos;s nephew and that&apos;s all. He becomes the son of Helen in the TV movie with David Suchet. And then it turns out, in the T<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In the book, George is Richard's nephew and that's all. He becomes the son of Helen in the TV movie with David Suchet. And then it turns out, in the TV movie I mean, he's Richard's son with Helen, instead of Leo's son with Helen.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
